  "keyFeatures": [
    "Double-buffered rendering with minimal I/O",
    "Pure functional architecture with zero classes",
    "Rich layout system with constraints (Length, Percentage, Ratio, Fill)",
    "Full style system with 16 ANSI, 256-color, and 24-bit RGB support",
    "10+ built-in widgets (Block, List, Table, Gauge, Sparkline, etc.)",
    "React-like JSX API for declarative UI composition",
    "Wide character (CJK) support",
    "TypeScript strict mode with complete type safety"
  ],
